        <ul>
          <li>Building a tool that agents can call? → <strong>MCP</strong></li>
          <li>Building an agent that other agents can hire? → <strong>A2A</strong></li>
          <li>Building a production multi-agent system? → <strong>Both, at different layers</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

